skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: n. x. recipe
des:
This skill allows you to add items to your grocery list setup in the App.
After you use this skill to connect your account you can add additional items that may not be related to what you are planning to cook.

This skill is free, and there will never be any in-skill purchases.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
